divs: Sighting DetailsI had got off the interstate to get gas in Coffee Co. and went the wrong way down the road I drove about a mile or 2 thinking maybe there was a gas station on down that way but I ended up turning around and heading back up toward the interstate because the town must have been on up a good ways. While getting lost I noticed over a field area some strange lights at first I though it was a plane but it had 3 sometimes 4 white lights on it. They would come off and on in a pattern and a couple of times went out completely. This objected looked to be hovering and descending down slowly. I have no idea what was over that way and didn't want to find out! I pulled off and watched it a couple of minutes and I rolled down the window but didn't hear a sound. I got my gas and jumped back on the interstate and headed home! I don't know what that object was but I never seen something that large not make some kind of noise and the light pattern was not like a plane or heli.
Summary: Object with 3 or 4 white lights hovering Coffee Co.
